notes: Interrupts the user's channeling spells upon cast.

Creates regular trees at the caster's location on every server tick. These trees are smaller than the other trees on the map and has a smaller collision size. Does not create trees when the caster's collision size overlaps with that of any other tree.
This means it blocks vision and is treated like any other tree by all abilities which interact with trees.
Tango heals for twice as long when targeting a Woodland Strider tree, using the ward duration instead of the tree duration.
The particles around the tree are visible to everyone, making it clear that it is a planted tree.
abilities.description: Create a path of trees behind you for 3 seconds. Trees last up to 60 seconds.
Removes movement speed limit and allows free pathing through trees.

info: Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.
Stacks with all other movement speed bonuses.
